48:34.833 --> 48:36.958
[Pieptöne]

48:39.667 --> 48:40.875
[Arthur] Oh, nein.

48:41.917 --> 48:43.958
Nein, nein, nein, nein. Nein.

48:48.875 --> 48:50.250
[weint] Tuttles.

48:57.208 --> 48:59.208
-[Pieptöne]
-[Arthur] Tuts.

